Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.13,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}疯狂吧{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}　Hey kids!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:38.15,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}同本应相遇的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.90,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}疯狂地哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:44.99,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}愿寻回那无法忘却的爱　长相厮守
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.70,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}疯狂吧{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}　Hey kids!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:50.53,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}就算如此未来也是虚幻的吗{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}？
